cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM. 

The paper presents a method for visual object classification using a single feature and a variant of Spatial Pyramid Matching. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as the primary sub-category. The method also involves training with an ensemble of linear regression, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves encoding and generating histograms, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
